---
title: Veggie Tacos Al Pastor with Warm Pineapple Salsa and Pickled Veggies
description: In this veggie twist on tacos al pastor, pork is swapped out for roasted, cumin-and-oregano-spiced sweet potato and poblano. Once the veggies are tender and lightly charred, they’re piled into steamy tortillas along with pickled onion and jalapeño, warm pineapple salsa, hot sauce crema, and a sprinkle of cilantro. Yep, Tuesday (any day) just got a whole lot better.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/veggie-tacos-al-pastor-0954d423.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/veggie-tacos-al-pastor-5da0cf5ef4ac697f602db663-6cad39b2.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/veggie-tacos-al-pastor-5da0cf5ef4ac697f602db663
cuisine: Mexican
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 730 kcal
